title: Prototype 2 DLC Packs for PC
description:
The two DLC packs for [PROTOTYPE 2] "Colossal Mayhem Pack" and "Excessive Force" ported to PC.

To install, simply extract both files to your Prototype 2 install directory (e.g. "C:Program Files (x86)SteamsteamappscommonPrototype 2"). I would suggest backing up the file that has to be overwritten.

Tested working on a legitimate Steam copy.  I would assume it would also work on a pirated copy.
